column2: Magnolia Oil & Gas Corp. is engaged in oil and gas exploration and production business. The company is headquartered in Houston, Texas and currently employs 27 full-time employees. The firm owns assets located in the Eagle Ford Shale and Austin Chalk formations in South Texas. The firm operates in Karnes County and Giddings Field. The company operates 14, 070 net acres in Karnes County and approximately 3,60,000 net acres in Giddings Field.
